esting and quality assurance consulting services which often take their time to sort out the procedure.</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\\\"ltr\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:30px;\\\"><b id=\\\"docs-internal-guid-6568e862-7fff-f2e1-216d-6076cda20efd\\\">Product Testing Stage</b></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><b id=\\\"docs-internal-guid-6568e862-7fff-f2e1-216d-6076cda20efd\\\"><img height=\\\"416\\\" src=\\\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/2FJNVAvUvLD1weSzi9lOBscnoZW8mNPXA1VjtcP15Y0gdV8dDQuFhymZTdD-1oInglgOYeCUBeBrLRpWIoM7AgnhZLFqDA9V0ThgEGwQsTfQl1-eLO4x1oR1nkFArE4rsKIw32EJ\\\" width=\\\"624\\\" /></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\\\"ltr\\\">The product testing stage permits a totally new arrangement of eyes, investigating the product application keeping in mind the end goal to test it in a genuine situation and far from the formal methodology that the standard programming advancement group does. Testing in this stage may include the testing of this product on different machines each with their different working frameworks. It likewise includes other useful software testing methodologies that distinguish that it is so natural to utilize the product.</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\\\"ltr\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:30px;\\\"><b id=\\\"docs-internal-guid-6568e862-7fff-f2e1-216d-6076cda20efd\\\">Beta Testing Stage</b></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><b id=\\\"docs-internal-guid-6568e862-7fff-f2e1-216d-6076cda20efd\\\"><img height=\\\"388\\\" src=\\\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/tAxqpAexEHqB1GZx14iUCF78Tl6sKzxJuMeaRkUybS3JFjtlPqsAg8kYueaadIrVXM4KeYOUdiFW-55f362KC9dXpfOhL2bVAet7x3fEONsd35VoN1JvySlDtznhOLnGSPdmjJsS\\\" width=\\\"500\\\" /></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\\\"ltr\\\">In some cases, the product will be discharged to the bigger open with a specific end goal to get a reaction that decides how proficient the product will be.</p>\