(24, 12, 'Performance Test Engineer', '', '', '', 'Experienced', '1', '4', 'Sector-63, Noida (UP) 201 301', 'Load testing, JProfiler, Performance testing, Rest, SOAP, Jmeter, DynaTrace, JRockit, JConsole, AppDynamics, Test scripts', '<p>AppSierra&nbsp;is seeking a motivated Performance Engineer who join a team of experts who are passionate and hands-on to be responsible for developing innovative solutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>-Creation of Jmeter test scripts for web and SOAP/REST web services<br />\r\n-Knowledge of profiling tools like Yourkit, Heap dump analysis, Memory profiling, JProfiler, JRockit, JConsole, DynaTrace, AppDynamics&nbsp;<br />\r\n-Knowledge of performance monitoring tools<br />\r\n-Knowledge of application performance tuning<br />\r\n-Analyze performance results analysis and identify bottlenecks<br />\r\n-Monitoring all performance runs with respect to CPU/memory/network/storage/IO&nbsp;<br />\r\n-Utilization trends for all products/services<br />\r\n-Performance executions in Performance Lab using Jmeter<br />\r\n-Suggest performance optimizations to products<br />\r\n-Proficient in troubleshooting application performance issues<br />\r\n-Proficient in scripting language such as UNIX Shell scripting and batch files&nbsp;<br />\r\n-Passionate to innovate &amp; implement ideas to address efficiency, best practices, improved processes, and cool solutions<br />\r\n-Good knowledge of clustering, high availability and monitoring<br />\r\n-Familiarity with Identity Management products e.g. LDAP servers, Access Management, Identity Management etc is a plus</p>\r\n', 0, '2018-09-04 07:01:40', 'Permanent', '906517'),
(25, 16, 'Mobile/Web Application Test Analyst ', '', '', '', 'Experienced', '2', '4', 'C-277, Rajdhani Corporate Suites, Sec-63, Noida', 'Selenium, Mobile application testing, Web application testing, Test scripts, Jmeter, SDLC, JAVA', '<ul class=\"listing mt10 wb\" itemprop=\"description\" style=\"padding:0px; margin:10px 0px 0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif; list-style:none; word-break:break-word; font-size:13px; line-height:18px; color:#666666; font-style:normal; font-variant-ligatures:normal; font-variant-caps:normal; font-weight:400; letter-spacing:normal; orphans:2; text-align:start; text-transform:none; white-space:normal; widows:2; word-spacing:0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; text-decoration-style:initial; text-decoration-color:initial\">\r\n	<li>- Hands on experience on&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">Mobile</font></font>/Web&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">Application</font></font>&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">Testing</font></font>.&nbsp;<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Experience in&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">testing</font></font>&nbsp;with different&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">Mobile</font></font>&nbsp;app OS (Android &amp; iOS)&nbsp;<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Familiarity with process and better understanding in SDLC, STLC, Agile-Scrum.&nbsp;<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Experience in creating&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">test</font></font>&nbsp;deliverables such as&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">Test</font></font>&nbsp;Strategies,<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">Test</font></font>&nbsp;scenarios, metrics and automation&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">test</font></font>&nbsp;scripts.&nbsp;<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Experience in using&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">testing</font></font>&nbsp;tools for load, performance(Jmeter)&nbsp;<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Document software defects, using a bug tracking system, and report defects to software developers and project managers.&nbsp;<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Monitor bug resolution efforts and track successes.&nbsp;<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- SQL and Relational Database&nbsp;<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	-&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">Test</font></font>&nbsp;Management tool knowledge (e.g. JIRA, Mantis)&nbsp;<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Microsoft office knowledge&nbsp;<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Understanding of the Software Development Lifecycle of&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">testing</font></font>&nbsp;Lifecycle&nbsp;<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Thorough knowledge of structured&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">test</font></font>&nbsp;methods and processes&nbsp;<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Capability to communicate in a clear and effective manner, both written and verbally.&nbsp;<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Knowledge of Java&nbsp;<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Working Knowledge of Selenium.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 0, '2018-10-05 12:28:01', 'Contract', '314598'),
(26, 15, 'Test Automation Engineer', '', '', '', 'Experienced', '1', '3', 'C-277, Rajdhani Corporate Suites, Sec-63, Noida', 'Selenium, Selenium RC, Selenium WebDriver, Selenium Grid, Maven, Gradle, ', '<p>3-5 years of experience in Selenium<br />\r\nGood knowledge on Selenium suite of Tools (Selenium IDE, Selenium RC, Selenium WebDriver and Selenium Grid)<br />\r\nStrong Java programming / scripting skills<br />\r\nStrong concepts on Maven and Gradle<br />\r\nHands on experience in developing/customizing various automation frameworks (Keyword driven, Hybrid etc.)<br />\r\nExcellent, debugging, problem-solving and root-cause analysis skills.<br />\r\nCo-coordinating Test team members and Development team in order to resolve the issues.<br />\r\nGood communication and interpersonal skills<br />\r\nAbility to provide technical guidance to junior-level test engineers</p>\r\n', 0, '2018-10-05 12:27:41', 'Permanent', '820615'),
(27, 16, 'Mobile Automation Test Engineer', '', '', '', 'Experienced', '2', '4', 'C-277, Rajdhani Corporate Suites, Sec-63, Noida', 'Mobile automation testing, Appium, Java, Selenium, iOS, Android, Maven, TestNG, Fiddler', '<ul class=\"listing mt10 wb\" itemprop=\"description\" style=\"padding:0px; margin:10px 0px 0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif; list-style:none; word-break:break-word; font-size:13px; line-height:18px; color:#666666; font-style:normal; font-variant-ligatures:normal; font-variant-caps:normal; font-weight:400; letter-spacing:normal; orphans:2; text-align:start; text-transform:none; white-space:normal; widows:2; word-spacing:0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; text-decoration-style:initial; text-decoration-color:initial\">\r\n	<li>-should be strong on Appium, Java, Selenium,&nbsp;iOS and Android.<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Should be able to make recommendations and build&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">automation</font></font>&nbsp;frameworks from scratch.<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Should be hands on and train other junior resources<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Programming experience with Java or any other object oriented language.<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Experience ib developing highly reusable and efficient&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">Test</font></font>&nbsp;frameworks.<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Should have experience&nbsp;in Database&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">testing</font></font>&nbsp;and Manual&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">testing</font></font><br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Knowledge of Software Development Life Cycle (Agile is a must to have)<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Hands on experience with Maven,&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">Test</font></font>NG and JIRA<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Knowledge of Web Analytics and&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">testing</font></font>&nbsp;of same using tools like Charles, Fiddler or Browser Mob will be an added advantage</li>\r\n	<li>- Experience in E-commerce domain will be plus<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Good communication skills both oral and written</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 0, '2018-10-05 12:27:21', 'Contract', '586497'),
(29, 11, 'Security Test Engineer', '', '', '', 'Experienced', '1', '3', 'C-277, Rajdhani Corporate Suites, Sec-63, Noida', 'Java, Ruby, Php, perl, Web technologies, Application security testing,  mobile testing, Penetration testing, Vulnerability Assessment', '<ul class=\"listing mt10 wb\" itemprop=\"description\" style=\"padding:0px; margin:10px 0px 0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif; list-style:none; word-break:break-word; font-size:13px; line-height:18px; color:#666666; font-style:normal; font-variant-ligatures:normal; font-variant-caps:normal; font-weight:400; letter-spacing:normal; orphans:2; text-align:start; text-transform:none; white-space:normal; widows:2; word-spacing:0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; text-decoration-style:initial; text-decoration-color:initial\">\r\n	<li>- Good understanding of all&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">security</font></font>&nbsp;related fundamentals, standards, compliances<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Should be familiar with Vulnerability Assessment, Penetration&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">testing</font></font>, Secure code review<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Minimum 2 -8 years of working experience in Conducting Application&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">Security</font></font>&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">Testing</font></font>&nbsp;and Source code review<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Basic script development in Java/.NET/Perl/Ruby/PhP/Python<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- In-depth experience in using Application&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">Security</font></font>&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">testing</font></font>&nbsp;tools like WebInspect, Burpsuite and others<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Experience in using scanners like HP fortify, Veracode, Checkmarx for Secure Source code review<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Relevant certifications (CEH/OSCP/CSSLP/CISSP) will be an added advantage<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Strong Communication skills.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong><u>Roles &amp; Responsibilities</u></strong></em>:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"listing mt10 wb\" itemprop=\"description\" style=\"padding:0px; margin:10px 0px 0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif; list-style:none; word-break:break-word; font-size:13px; line-height:18px; color:#666666; font-style:normal; font-variant-ligatures:normal; font-variant-caps:normal; font-weight:400; letter-spacing:normal; orphans:2; text-align:start; text-transform:none; white-space:normal; widows:2; word-spacing:0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; text-decoration-style:initial; text-decoration-color:initial\">\r\n	<li>Conduct vulnerability assessment and penetration&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">testing</font></font>&nbsp;for web and mobile applications.<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Conduct Secure Code review of Web and Mobile Applications<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Should be able to deal with multiple platforms like Windows, Linux and technologies like Java, .Net<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Conduct Threat Modelling of Applications<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Benchmark applications against&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">security</font></font>&nbsp;best practices<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Ability to analyse root causes and deliver strategic recommendations during&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">security</font></font>&nbsp;reviews<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Conduct&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">Security</font></font>&nbsp;Code Review, Penetration&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">Testing</font></font>&nbsp;and Consult Product Development Team to secure applications<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Being a&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">Security</font></font>&nbsp;Consultant for delivering complete project life cycles - from capturing Customer requirements to delivering timely solutions to Customers<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	<br style=\"padding:0px; margin:0px; font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\" />\r\n	- Adhering to best practices, and alignment with the Customers&nbsp;<font class=\"hlite\"><font style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 700;\">security</font></font>&nbsp;requirements for project execution, documentation, and reporting</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 0, '2018-10-05 12:26:58', 'Contract', '894327'),
(30, 17, 'QA Engineer', 'Quality Analyst', 'Best in the Industry', '', 'Experienced', '1', '3', 'C-277, Rajdhani Corporate Suites, Sec-63, Noida', 'Manual Testing, API, JIRA, Test cases, SDLC, STLC', '<h3>Skills: Manual Testing, API, JIRA, Test cases, SDLC, STLC</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Should have 1-3 years&nbsp;of experience.</li>\r\n	<li>Should be involved in Design and documenting formal Test Procedures and Test Plans.</li>\r\n	<li>Knowledge &amp; experience in Manual Test Cases, Test Scenarios Development, Scripting.</li>\r\n	<li>Should have experience in Agile methodologies.</li>\r\n	<li>Should provide technical testing support during the SDLC, using SQL reporting tools to test data processing through applications and networks.</li>\r\n	<li>Organizational and time management abilities.</li>\r\n	<li>Analytical thinking, problem-solving and decision making.</li>\r\n	<li>Good Communication skill.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Salary:&nbsp;Best in the Industry.</p>\r\n', 0, '2018-10-05 12:43:20', 'Permanent', '143057');
