INSERT INTO `whitepapers` (`wp_id`, `wp_title`, `wp_img`, `wp_pdf`, `wp_date`, `wp_desc`) VALUES
(1, 'COMPATIBILITY TESTING ', '5baead8d1828c.png', 'COMPATIBILITY-TESTING.pdf', '2018-09-28 22:40:43', ''),
(2, 'SCRUM Take Quality To The Next Level', '5baeaec40e707.png', 'SCRUM-Take-Quality-To-The-Next-Level.pdf', '2018-09-28 22:44:20', ''),
(3, 'Testing Approach for Web Accessibility  ', '5bbb38d6254a2.png', 'Testing-Approach-for-Web-Accessibility.pdf', '2018-10-08 11:00:38', ''),
(4, 'OFFSHORE SOFTWARE TEST AUTOMATION', '5c08c2df82cf8.png', 'OFFSHORE-SOFTWARE-TEST-AUTOMATION.pdf', '2018-12-06 06:34:07', 'This particular white paper presents an executive overview of a creative perspective to\r\nintegrating global resourcing and the newest test automation techniques and tools. This\r\nmethodology can surprisingly help any software development agency fulfil their\r\ngoals of time-to-market, cost containment and quality.'),
(5, 'The Art Of Keyword Driven Testing', '5c0f5908acf21.png', 'The-Art-Of-Keyword-Driven-Testing.pdf', '2018-12-11 06:28:25', 'Keyword-Driven testing has helped us for  ages but, like everything else, it\r\nkeeps developing with time. This paper inspects the common mistakes in implementing Keyword-Driven Testing solutions.'),
(6, 'Software Testing 3.0: The Ongoing Evolution Of Software Testing', '5c135b8d375fc.png', 'Software-Testing-3.0:-The-Ongoing-Evolution-Of-Software-Testing.pdf', '2018-12-14 07:28:13', 'This particular paper will take you through the constant improvement of software testing, specifically the first two phases after which we are going to present the recent state of the practice: Software Testing 3.0, which is an innovative and strategic approach to software quality assurance.'),
(7, 'Avoiding The Pitfalls Of Test Automation', '5c1b4a2f5b7f6.png', 'Avoiding-The-Pitfalls-Of-Test-Automation.pdf', '2018-12-20 07:52:15', 'Test automation has the capability to increase the speed for the release cycles, expand coverage and finally deliver greater confidence in the quality of the software being released. However, software test automation can be an expensive investment with very low returns if not executed in the right way.\r\nThis paper brings into limelight the challenges that are not currently obvious but are more clear in the initial stages of implementing test automation and provides steps that can be taken to avoid the blunders or take the correct decision.\r\n'),
(8, 'SCRUM, Take Quality To The Next Level', '5c23397ecf084.png', 'SCRUM,-Take-Quality-To-The-Next-Level.pdf', '2018-12-26 08:19:10', 'All sports enthusiasts know how vital a formation is, it brings success to a football team as well as a rugby team. It can similarly bring about success in the software industry. In the software industry terms, for every customer\\\'s requirement, there is a need for a customized formation. \r\n'),
(9, 'COMPATIBILITY TESTING- A VITAL NECESSITY FOR WEB APPS', '5c374515f17ac.png', 'COMPATIBILITY-TESTING--A-VITAL-NECESSITY-FOR-WEB-APPS.pdf', '2019-01-10 13:13:59', 'In Todayâ€™s time, technology-driven businesses, demand a software application to work along with a wide range of hardware configurations, operating systems, web browsers & browser versions. Systematic compatibility testing is critical for businesses to make their products compatible with all or most of their end users.'),
(10, 'Testing Approach For Web Accessibility', '5c4170e9ab240.jpeg', 'Testing-Approach-For-Web-Accessibility.pdf', '2019-01-18 06:23:37', 'The potential of this paper is to mark the access barriers, challenges and risks involved in the testing approach by following accessibility rules and how to overcome them by using the web accessibility testing approach thereby testing whether the website is accessible to everyone or not. Our approach elucidates the effectiveness of open source evaluation tool and human judgment involvement in accessibility testing.\r\n');
